This class manages the page build process. Based on which features the respective observation
station provides, the page is built differently. There is a configuration file which says which
diagrams must be drawn for which features. Accordingly the page is built.
Must be initialized with a Feature. The observationStation can be set afterwards, as
well as the data of the diagram can be loaded. When all the necessary data is loaded,
the diagram can be drawn and becomes visable in the userinterface.
This allowes asynchronous page loading from outside of this class.
